2004-07-06 12:53  d2uhlman

	* admin/categories/delete.php:

	deleting a company didn't, the update query wasn't being generated becuase the supplied value for category_record_status was empty, now it is updated to NULL. It didn't look like any other value than a is used for it, presumably a for active, so NULL is a good choice for deleted

